page.title: 11LANDSCAPE - PHOTOGRAPH A
page.content: Physical landscape -Glacial and/or fluvio-glacial deposits from Loch Lomond re-advance during later stages of the glacial epoch. Glacier moved left to right . Centre - Coltness High School(opened late 1960's).Behind this across photo. trees of old Mossneuk Plantation(Coltness Estate).Centre and left private houses of Mossneuk Estate (pre-1939). Right of centre and front of school council houses - Thrashbush area(built 1950's).Centre left just visible between the trees council houses - Coltness East(built 1950's). Bottom right corner Cambusnethan Primary School .
